{"tid":772759,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【兔迷】兔仔開心到極!! 身體語言+室內養會長壽!","createTime":"2018-08-09T04:27:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T05:01:17.000Z","uid":197098,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c74653f24eaee767709f3a4b794f58f70ad4f061","tid":772759,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:27:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">兔子跳兔子舞(Binky)是兔子最開心的狀態。當牠們binky 時，這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活。兔子也會舒適地躺在地上，伸展手腳，還會打翻騰。兔子在室內飼養會比室外養長命，因為沒有任何天氣和敵人威脅，感到平靜和舒適。狗吠聲、雷暴、消防車叫聲等也會嚇驚兔子。以下2個videos 可以看到兔子最開心的時候：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E90ikFGQTqs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DE90ikFGQTqs&d=fsGHaT9mmPjonTOwxUe9fjACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=50020070\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E90ikFGQTqs</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FDMWC5U0gkw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFDMWC5U0gkw&d=fsGHaT9mmPjonTOwxUe9fjACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=93b5f3b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FDMWC5U0gkw</a> </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>領養兔仔，不要買！</ins></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">實在有太多主人遺棄兔子，主要原因是不理解兔子,覺得牠們悶不親近人。兔子是聰明、群體性動物。如果想養，可在兔友協會領養，這裏有太多兔子需要一個家。詳情可去 <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=fsGHaT9mmPjonTOwxUe9fjACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=527b0ced\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a> </span>"},{"pid":"69caba8f6f413d9e86705630ac2e90edbf254e23","tid":772759,"uid":188310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:51:27.000Z","msg":"一般兔壽命有幾長"},{"pid":"52692275ff1aacdab42910dc58f05d89ee8a0735","tid":772759,"uid":177089,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTi